RULES_TEXT = 'Kill the enemy king!\n\nPlace your king on the edge at game start,\n\nDraw paths to place new army camps,\n\nDraw one main path or multiple shorter paths from neighboring camps,\n\nAttack from army camps to displace enemy camps and cut enemy roads.\n\nElevation matters! Attacks must come from the high ground!\n\nHowever, if an enemy group is cut off from its command, its nodes and roads may be attacked from any elevation!\n\nTo gain ground, fortify one of your connected paths, or sap the ground around a node.\n\nCreated by Roman Dowling, 2026'

